title: Moving Pictures - Matinee
description:
Moving Pictures' second album, Matinee, was released in October 1983 and reached number 16 in Australia. With a strong live following, the band toured Japan before band problems saw Frost leave and eventually form 1927. Joey Amenta served as a temporary replacement for Frost until Kevin Bennett joined the lineup
